window.bookSummaryJSON = "Sir Claud Amory has discovered the formula for a new powerful explosive, which is stolen by one of the large household of relatives and friends. <p>Locking everyone in the library, Sir Claud switches off the lights to allow the thief to replace the formula on the table, no questions asked.</p> <p>When the lights come on, however, he is dead, and Hercule Poirot, with assistance from Hastings and Inspector Japp, has to unravel a tangle of family feuds, old flames, and suspicious foreigners to find the killer and prevent a global catastrophe.</p>"; 
